                        <p style="text-align: center; " data-mce-style="text-align: center;"><span class="figure image-left" style="width:275px;"><img data-copyright-style="inverted" src="https://www.ovg.ox.ac.uk/images/images/studyparticipant.png/@@images/2168588d-0638-4271-804a-a82f85d35bd6.png" title="A Study Participant" data-mce-src="resolveuid/bcc16bb45b494fb980c8d6c84a051bc4/@@images/image/w275" data-src="https://www.ovg.ox.ac.uk/images/images/studyparticipant.png" alt="A study participant" /></span><strong>Find <em>your</em> study</strong></p><p style="text-align: center; " data-mce-style="text-align: center;">Browse our studies below to find one that's right for you. Not eligable for our current studies? Join our Newsletter to be the first to find out about new studies when they start.</p><p style="text-align: center; " data-mce-style="text-align: center;">Jump toÂ  <a target="_self" title="" data-class-override="btn btn-warning bottom-margin-3px" href="https://www.ovg.ox.ac.uk/recruiting-studies#adult-studies" data-mce-href="recruiting-studies#adult-studies">Adult Studies</a>Â Â  or Â  <a target="_self" title="" data-class-override="btn btn-warning bottom-margin-3px" href="https://www.ovg.ox.ac.uk/recruiting-studies#children-s-studies" data-mce-href="recruiting-studies#children-s-studies">Children's Studies</a></p><p style="text-align: center; " data-mce-style="text-align: center;">or read our <a title="" href="https://www.ovg.ox.ac.uk/privacy-notice" data-mce-href="resolveuid/792e0857653d4aaba396bc00d7d72703" target="_self">Privacy Notice</a></p>
                    
                
